						<div class="postbody">Hmm I don't have a problem with split roms in a container, it's certainly better than a database... If this had to be done, it would be nice to have a zip file containing a "PRG" file or few, a "CHR" file if applicable, a "BOARD"/"PCB"/"MMC"/something (which is only plaintext board name) and other files for whatever else is appropriate for that game. (Just not TOO much detail)</div>

